Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是个好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
