Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whoa, whoa! Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 嘿 别激动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, hey. Hey, take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我装傻 你在机车里干什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't play dumb. What were you doing in the Engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的麻烦大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're in a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. Hey, hey, hey. No, no, no. Hey. Hey. Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我不知道你们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, I don't know what you--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hello, chaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 嘿 老天 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey! Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈 刚才好险啊 搜他身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That was too close, Andre. Clean him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-哈维  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Javi? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你拿到了吗  -拿到什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Have you got it? - Got what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁丝 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ruth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 别破坏气氛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, shut up. - You're ruining this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嗯 在他身上 -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. He's got it. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-撤吧 这会招来麻烦的 -冷静点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. Let's clear out. - This'll draw heat. - Calmly now. Calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们分头行动 在边境汇合 所有人都带着过境文件吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We split up and meet at the border. Everybody got their papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-带着 -很好 来吧 我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. - Good. Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-鲁丝 -走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温妮 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Winnie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何不可呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提尔 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Till. Wow. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你得帮帮我 我需要…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you gotta help me. I need--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小声点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inside voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场噩梦已经做得够久了 我得醒过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that's about enough of this nightmare. I have to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 伙计 你得打起精神 好吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, buddy, you gotta get your shit together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在做梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是快死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嗨 -嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明了 守夜结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's first light. - The vigil's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把他叫出来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's go get our boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的脉搏很弱 去找裴尔顿医生 快去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- His pulse is weak. - Go and get Dr. Pelton. Quick, quick, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14} Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wake up. Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嘿 -醒过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. - Wake up. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 冷静点 否则你会害我们俩都进大牢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cool it, or you'll get us both thrown in the slammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里你不能胡来 明白吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't mess around here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“这里”是哪里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这不是雪国列车 -这里是 但也不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is not Snowpiercer. - No, it is. And it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会认出这里的人 但他们跟那一边的不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll recognize people, but they're not the same as they are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你几乎是一样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're the same. Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是图书管理员 我很博学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm the librarian. I know things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上还带着另一边的残留物 但它们会退去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're still carrying residue from the other side. But it will fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会习惯这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You'll get used to it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习惯 不 提尔 我得回家去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. "Used to it"? No. Till, I need to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家 那就不同了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh. Well, that's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那事儿我帮不上忙 -为什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think I can help you with that. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 你得去见末等车厢老大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, first, you'd have to see the Tail Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但去那的路上很危险 明白我的意思吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's a dangerous journey, you know want I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nope, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 听好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. Work with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想回去 就得找到末等车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want to get back, you need to find the Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求末等车厢老大把你送回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and ask the Tail Boss to send you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔福德 他刚才假装是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford, he was pretending to be my buddy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算越过边境处理什么事务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he was gonna cross the border for some mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我需要过境文书\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I needed papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这个我能帮上忙 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh. Now, that I can help you with. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-跟我来 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Follow me. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 数到三 一 二 三\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay, on three. One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么样了 医生怎么说 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How is he? Well, what does the doctor say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时没消息 医生此刻跟雷顿在一起 我们刚把他送来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nothing yet. - She's with him now. We only just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前说不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said everything was gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔西 发生什么事了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道 这…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…怎么都叫不醒他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He just--he just wouldn't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赝造师就在下一扇门里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The forger's the next door down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-别让他知道你不是这里的人 -你不一起来吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't let on you're not from here. - You're not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿 我没法带你去末等车厢 听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't get you to the Tail, Layton. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里的时间越长 回另一边去的难度就越大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The longer you're here, the harder it is to get to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别迷路了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是干什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What did you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在阳世的时间不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have much time in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你开始迷路 这个伤口会给你指路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This cut will guide you if you start to lose your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该谢谢你 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thanks, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 祝你好运 伙计 你会需要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. Good luck, bud. You'll need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我需要过境文书 -别在走廊里说这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Uh, I'm here for my papers. - Not in the hall. - Not in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想来一杯吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（临时旅行证）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始让你厌烦了吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Starts to wear on you, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编的故事说多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You tell yourself your cover story
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己都开始忘记什么是真的 什么是编的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so many times, you start to forget what's real and what you made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不这么认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从没相信过自己编的谎言 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never started to believe your own lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便吧 你无需向我证明你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever, you don't have to prove yourself to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经退出江湖了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am out of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是一份让我坚持下去的小小副业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is just a little side hustle to keep me going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里签字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sign here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有了这个 我就能去末等车厢  -末等车厢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This will get me in the Tail? - The Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你想寻死吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What, you got a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上恰恰相反\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, just the opposite, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不掺和末等车厢的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't mess with the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想去末等车厢 就得去找制图师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want the Tail, go see the Cartographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制图师 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cartographer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 去市场找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes. In the Market.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要一些东西作为回报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna need something in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两名特工在列车前列遇害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two operatives got whacked uptrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你参与了此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard that you were involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得扣动扳机的另有其人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I figure someone else pulled the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把开枪的人的名字告诉我 我就把过境文书给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you give me the triggerman's name, and I will send you on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 知道我也不做告密的小人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, and I don't rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文书你留着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep your damn papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁丝 这里是怎么回事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's going on here, Ruth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个小小的考验 你之前搞砸了 被人抓了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just a little test. You screwed up and got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们得确认是否还能信任你 -你有答案了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to know we can trust you. - You have your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会盯着你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I got my eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有消息吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Any news?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他情况稳定 你们可以进去看他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's stable. - You can see him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事没有委婉的表达方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's no sugarcoating this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他处于昏迷中 已经长达12小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's in a coma, has been for up to 12 hours already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会醒过来吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Will he wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我能回答你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I wish I could tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CT扫描显示脑部有些肿胀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}CT scan shows some brain swelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他的瞳孔有反应 这是个好迹象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but his pupils are responding, so that's a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们现在要怎么办 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持坚强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握着他的手 跟他说说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hold his hand, talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕除了等待 没其他办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a waiting game, I'm afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但欢迎你们留下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you're welcome to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有消息及时通知我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You keep us updated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得回机车了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to get back to the Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. I'll come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没必要离开 他会希望你留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You don't have to. He'd want you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他通过考验了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然通过考验了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Course I passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟 我跟她说你很靠谱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told her you were solid, sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让我失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我准备好了 我们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. I'm good. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们一个一个地过境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Right. We cross the border individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答问题时只用“是”或“不是”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Answer questions yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要伪装的身份不穿帮 就不会有事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stick to your cover stories. We should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我的伪装身份是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. - Uh, what's my cover story?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是开玩笑吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我只是忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, I'm fine. I just forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行事谨慎些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, tighten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个舞者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're a dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-约瑟夫威尔福德 -此行的目的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Joseph Wilford. - Purpose of travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（现代舞表演 晚上8点）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进出口 外国水果和糖品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Import-export. - Exotic fruit and sugars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈雷顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Andre Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我刚…安德烈雷顿 -你为什么会来列车前列 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I just--Andre Layton. - Why were you uptrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个舞者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm a dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢芭蕾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I love the ballet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其实我是跳现代舞的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, it's modern, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有演出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had a recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞蹈是身体及灵魂…隐藏的语言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dance is the hidden language of the body...and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜我错过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sad I missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次呗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该在这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You shouldn't be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我只是想静一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, I'm just hiding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我可以离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I--I can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地方都是你的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说雷顿的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard about Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我很难过 -你会难过才怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm very sorry. - Yeah, I'm sure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前从没见你哭过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never seen you cry before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用强忍住伤心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, you don't have to fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你最好的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在这样 我却无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And there's nothing I can do to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你走吧 奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So--bye, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以跟他说说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You could talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他的意识还在就能听到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he's still in there, he'll hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提醒他他为之奋斗的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remind him what he's fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事应该你来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你以前在夜车做的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like you used to in the Nightcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能影响他人的想法和感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You get inside people's heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的专长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's your thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟那个不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才还说值得一试呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just told me it's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了…奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老约 鲁丝 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Joe. Ruthie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来这里我太高兴了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you have just made my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get down here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是顺路拜访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're just dropping in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下 来吧 伙计们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brief respite. Come on, chaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲爱的 你真是光彩照人呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You, my dear, are radiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为湿润 让皮肤变得有光泽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It is the humidity. - It makes me glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能在这里待多久  我留着你最喜欢的桌位呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, how long do I get to keep you? Come, I've got your favorite table waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少到傍晚时分吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Till the sun's over the yard, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 过来吧 来呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, hey. - Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我们两杯烈酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two shots, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了礼节了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You forgot your manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是朗姆酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's rum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说 有问题吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No shit. That a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是…让我想起了往事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it just, um, takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh. Check it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去一下洗手间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 稍等一下 我们聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, wait a minute. - Let's have a chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁丝 看在老天的份上 让他喘口气吧 抱歉了 老伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- For God's sake, Ruth. - Let him breathe. Sorry, old chap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一杯朗姆酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Another rum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我在找制图师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, I'm looking for the cartographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-来顶帽子吧 -好 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帽子很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你迷路了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是制图师 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're the cartographer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 进来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗盯着我看 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你让我想起了一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. Sorry. - You remind me of someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你想去哪儿  -末等车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where you trying to go? - The Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么想去那儿 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why you want to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我的家人身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get back to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你有孩子 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah? You're a dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有个女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当了父母 你就会做出疯狂的事来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, being a parent makes you do crazy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样…到末等车厢那里去不是难事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So getting to the Tail, that's the easy part.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要进去 就得知道暗号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Getting in the Tail, you need the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 暗号是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. What's the word?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道暗号是什么 不过 “多数人会避开 有些人会寻求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't know the word, but..."Most will run, some will seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是躲是骗 你我总会邂逅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Hide or cheat, we always meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把当下 过去和未来守候”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I present, past and future keep."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个谜语吗 我讨厌猜谜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is that a riddle? - Oh, I hate riddles. - Okay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-够了 -再说一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Give it to me again. - That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey, hey, hey. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just let go of my arm. Man! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14} - Gracias. - All yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:18:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说不能相信他吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I told you he stunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-别激动 我只是有点私事要办 -理由不够充分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy, okay? I just had some personal business. Oh, you're gonna have to do better than that, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞砸了取货的事 忘了自己的密码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You botched the pick-up, you forgot your password,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我知道 你跟赝造师谈过末等车厢的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I know that you talked to the Forger earlier about the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你做了担保 你告诉我说不会瞎问问题的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I vouched for you, Andre. You told me you wouldn't ask any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在保护自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I was just covering my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干了他得了 我们冒不起这种风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's pop him. We can't risk this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这玩意拿开 叫他们退下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get that shit out of my face. You tell them to stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-否则你不会带我到这里来 -我们只需要你安排会面的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or you never would've brought me this far. We only need you for the meeting, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后你我就两不相干了 明白吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After that, we're done. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我没问题 -鲁丝 把枪放下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fine by me. - Put the gun down, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道的事可能会伤害到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you don't know might hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有问题 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They're okay, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就他一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他带过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看呀 他出现了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at that, he showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是 计划不就是这样的吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That was the plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我们该客气点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, we're gonna be friends here, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-见到你真高兴 -我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good to see you. - You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你饿吗 你总是喊饿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. You hungry? You're always hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们给你弄点蟹螯吧 给这边来点蟹螯 蟹腿和牡蛎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, let's get you some claws. Some claws, some legs, oysters over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牡蛎和蟹螯 马上来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oysters, claws, coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-山姆… -这位…山姆…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sam. - This is--Sam,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这是约瑟夫威尔福德 -叫老约\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is Joseph Wilford. - Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老约 这位就是我跟你提起的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Joe. This is the guy I was telling you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很快会知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I guess we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开吃吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go ahead. Dive in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是来这里吃海鲜或找人作伴的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm not really here for the seafood or the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹是肮脏的生物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The crab's a filthy creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾警告过我 说我不会喜欢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He warned me I wouldn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是这么跟我说的 老伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said the same about you, old chap,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我告诉他这并不重要 反正我会忘记你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I told him it doesn't really matter, 'cause I'll forget you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了列车前列的枪击事件 两名特工被杀 这对这笔买卖很不利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard about that heat uptrain. Two dead G-men. That kind of sours the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事怨我 现场没有目击证人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, hey, that's on me. There were no witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老约帮我摆脱了困境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Joe bailed me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们顺利过了边境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got us across the border clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我要的东西能到手 我不在乎这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's not my problem, as long as I get what I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来检查一下吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's have a look. Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很正宗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's legit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭我被赋予的权力 你们几个混蛋被捕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- By the power vested in me, you assholes are under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 别这样 不要 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! No, don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现代舞表演 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Modern dance recital?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.49,0:23:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个儿童舞蹈团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was the kids' troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在麻烦大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're in a world of trouble now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是跟那边的你一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why am I not surprised you're like this over here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.47,0:24:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行刑安排在午夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Firing squad's at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.05,0:24:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 行刑 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wait. Hey, hey. - Firing squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.39,0:24:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.82,0:24:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想获得宽恕吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you want forgiveness?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.78,0:24:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派克 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pike?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.70,0:24:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.00,0:24:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此 兄弟 你的大限快到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Indeed, brother. Your hour draws nigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.71,0:24:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承认你的罪孽 你就会获得宽恕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Confess your sins, and you will be absolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.17,0:24:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么罪孽 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.88,0:24:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐厅里有一堆尸体 就从这事开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are a pile of bodies in the cantina. Start there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.89,0:24:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.35,0:24:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How can you get back home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.81,0:25:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己在找的是什么 你要怎么回家呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you don't even know what you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.40,0:25:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,末等车厢老大能送我回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Tail Boss can send me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.36,0:25:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点你就大错特错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's where you're very wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.28,0:25:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟想要我做什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you really want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.07,0:25:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当时威胁到了新伊甸园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You threatened New Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.74,0:25:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我别无选择 派克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't have any choice, Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.91,0:25:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿上帝怜悯你的灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May God have mercy on your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.50,0:25:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 派克 我赢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. Pike. Pike, I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.09,0:25:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有资格保守我的秘密 派克  这是说好的事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get to keep my secrets, Pike! That was the deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.01,0:25:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派克 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pike!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.94,0:25:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的情况如何 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.65,0:25:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有好转\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No change.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.48,0:25:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她来这里干什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.94,0:25:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 扎拉 但你跟着她在夜车做过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh. I know, Zarah. But you worked with her in the Nightcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.57,0:25:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她的能耐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what she can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.78,0:26:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是否会有效果 但我可以试试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know if it'll work, but I can try.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.95,0:26:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没有坏处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Guess it couldn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.33,0:26:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我可以去歇口气 -是呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I could use a break. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.83,0:26:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔西 你想去喝杯咖啡吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Josie, want to get a cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.00,0:26:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.34,0:26:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 现在要怎么做 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. Now what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.81,0:26:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我试着跟他沟通 -好 开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I try to reach him. - Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.24,0:26:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.53,0:26:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.37,0:26:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听听自己的呼吸声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.20,0:26:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受空气随着每一个呼吸 进出于你的肺部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feel the in and out as the air fills your lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.30,0:27:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈 如果你能听到我说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Andre, if you can hear me,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.97,0:27:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就朝我的声音过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}move towards my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.89,0:27:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想你身体的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.52,0:27:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想女儿在你怀里的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The feel of your daughter in your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.94,0:27:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想你爱的人在你耳边低语的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone you love whispering in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.69,0:27:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想你自己的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.03,0:27:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在寻找一样东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14} You're searching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.62,0:27:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不知道具体是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14} but you don't know what.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.50,0:27:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈 你被困住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're trapped, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.58,0:27:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在抓着不真实的东西不肯放手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're holding onto something that isn't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.25,0:27:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我这里来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14} Move towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.26,0:27:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.97,0:27:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管拖住你的东西是什么…去面对它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever's keeping you here, face it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.72,0:27:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.81,0:28:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈 你来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Andre. You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.90,0:28:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.53,0:28:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在出去的时候中了一枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I caught a bullet on the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.74,0:28:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得继续前进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've got to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.58,0:28:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.54,0:28:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去末等车厢 你就快到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- To the Tail. You're nearly there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.83,0:28:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.54,0:28:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.42,0:28:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.80,0:29:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们给末等车厢老大的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's our gift to the Tail Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.97,0:29:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝好运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.49,0:30:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我熟悉你这样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I recognize this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.95,0:30:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说明你对某个想法着了迷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've glommed on to some theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.08,0:30:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第一步 “疯狂地研究”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is step one, "research frenzy."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.42,0:30:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二步会是“浸泡在浴缸里” 如果你有浴缸的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Step two would be "soak in the bathtub" if you had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.21,0:30:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了 怎么回事  -或许其实没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So what is it? - Could be nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.09,0:30:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定有所发现 否则你不会叫我过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, it's clearly something because you called me in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.68,0:30:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉 我需要航图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I need charts, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.97,0:30:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我的工具 平行尺 指南针\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my instruments-- parallel ruler, compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.18,0:30:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好用来割破看守的喉咙 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that you can slash your guard in the throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.93,0:30:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷顿先生真的生命垂危吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it true Mr. Layton is at death's door?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.77,0:30:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你不需要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's need-to-know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.14,0:30:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 政治的事我不掺和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fine. Leave me out of the politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.23,0:30:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个…这是重大发现 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this...this is big, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.23,0:30:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给大家真正的希望 尤其是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give everyone some real hope, especially you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.07,0:30:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不帮我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.49,0:30:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可能永远都不会知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we may never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.33,0:30:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伊凡的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Old Ivan's Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.33,0:31:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.42,0:31:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本不该走到对决这一步的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wasn't supposed to go to knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.30,0:31:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天 我痛恨末等车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- God, I hated the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.68,0:31:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有那些习俗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All of its customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.18,0:31:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如把上下铺当钢琴弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like people playing the piano like it wasn't a bunk bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.06,0:31:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时 安德烈会教孩子们 如何繁殖老鼠 好当我们的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meanwhile, Andre's teaching children how to breed rats just so we can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.02,0:31:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那度过了一些黑暗的日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, we had some dark times.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.65,0:31:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.94,0:31:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你和安德烈 把大家照顾得非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you know, you and Andre took such good care of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.28,0:31:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩 你们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, the two of you just--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.74,0:31:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能激发出对方最好的一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you really bring out the best in each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.86,0:31:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我可不确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.41,0:31:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.08,0:31:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点曾让我深受威胁 可现在不会了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, it used to really threaten me, but it doesn't anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.21,0:31:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起当情侣 我和安德烈更适合合作当父母\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Andre and I are better as co-parents than as a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.38,0:31:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔西…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Josie...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.30,0:31:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不该出卖你的 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never should have turned my back on you. I--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.72,0:31:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你当时受到胁迫 别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. You were backed against a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.85,0:31:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不怪你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.81,0:32:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没怪过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.73,0:32:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有你在这里陪着我 我很高兴 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just so glad you're here with me today. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.49,0:32:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很高兴安德烈能有你作伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm glad that Andre has you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.55,0:32:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.67,0:32:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.51,0:32:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔西 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.39,0:32:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.26,0:32:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是末等车厢老大吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're the Tail Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.51,0:32:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没回答我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.14,0:32:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别 嘿…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.93,0:32:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫安德烈雷顿 我想回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My name is Andre Layton, and I'm trying to get back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.94,0:32:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识我吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.23,0:32:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识 但末等车厢老大认识每一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, but the Tail Boss knows everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.28,0:32:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“多数人会避开 有些人会寻求 不管是躲是骗 你我总会邂逅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Most will run, but some will seek. "But hide or cheat, we'll always meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.70,0:32:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把当下 过去和未来守候”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I present, past and future keep."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.37,0:32:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.95,0:33:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-乔西… -我是谁 雷顿先生 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie. - Who am I, Mr. Layton?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.29,0:33:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.38,0:33:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你 我没想到你会知道暗号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Been expecting you. Didn't think you'd know the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.84,0:33:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 我…事实上对此非常清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. I guess. I know it too well, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.27,0:33:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我是在试图逃避死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess I'm trying to escape it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.56,0:33:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡不是你的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Death isn't the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.56,0:33:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里是因为你在害怕一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're here 'cause you're scared of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.61,0:33:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.82,0:33:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在害怕什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What am I afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.49,0:33:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 但你得去面对它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't know, but you're gonna have to face it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.74,0:33:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.51,0:33:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这列车由你统管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You run the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.18,0:33:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.51,0:34:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大权在末等车厢 前后颠倒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The power's in the Tail. - It's upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.93,0:34:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有什么前后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- There's no up, no down.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.81,0:34:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这列车周而复始 是一个残酷的循环\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The train is cyclical. It's a cruel loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.94,0:34:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我看到地图了 是一条衔尾蛇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Right. - I saw the map. A snake eating its tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.94,0:34:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么才能跳出这个循环呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do I get back out of a loop?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.16,0:34:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以出去了 乔西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.66,0:34:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.16,0:34:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事说来复杂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.33,0:34:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事永远不像看上去那么复杂 带礼物来了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's never as complicated as it seems. You bring me a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.84,0:34:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有东西要给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have something for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.22,0:34:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是扎拉的笔迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's Zarah's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.26,0:34:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念给我听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Read it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.56,0:34:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我的小心肝…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"My little soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.03,0:34:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我还没见过你的脸 也没有抱过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I haven't seen your face yet or held you in my arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.99,0:35:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我对你的爱早已无穷无尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"but my love for you is already limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.87,0:35:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不光是我的孩子 你还是我们的未来”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You aren't just my child. You're the future."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.42,0:35:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是丽雅娜 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Liana?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.05,0:35:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.47,0:35:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.30,0:35:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这不是你的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, this is-- this isn't your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.89,0:35:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 为了你 我要回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not. I'm going back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.18,0:35:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能把你解救出来 打破这个循环\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I--I can get you out of this. I can break the cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.31,0:35:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你给我的礼物是什么吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Look at what you brought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.90,0:35:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里不是为了面对自己的大限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not here to face your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.99,0:35:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是派克的炸弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pike's bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.24,0:35:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是来面对我的大限的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're here to face mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.16,0:35:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽雅娜 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Liana! Liana!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.09,0:36:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈 醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Andre. Andre, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.89,0:36:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做噩梦了吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was a rough one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.35,0:36:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Asha?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.98,0:36:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会在这里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.81,0:36:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽雅娜应该把我送回家的呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Liana was supposed to send me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.90,0:36:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是你的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.36,0:36:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我应该在雪国列车上的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I'm supposed to be on Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.45,0:36:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地狱就是你唯一的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This hell is the only home you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.38,0:36:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快要找到答案了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm close to the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.51,0:36:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看那里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't look in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.47,0:36:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lunch is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.35,0:36:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,番茄汤和烤奶酪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tomato soup and a grilled cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.56,0:37:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想起了往事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.02,0:37:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我们不该流连于往事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, we shouldn't dwell on the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.07,0:37:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是设法活下去就够我们操心的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got enough to worry about just trying to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.70,0:37:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里头是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.66,0:37:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你有什么事瞒着我  -安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you keeping from me? - Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.25,0:37:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.00,0:37:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把钥匙给我 -别 不要 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me the key. - No. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.71,0:37:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-给… -放手 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.84,0:37:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Asha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.34,0:37:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 快住手 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.72,0:37:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的东西你不会喜欢的 明白吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not gonna like what you find in there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.52,0:37:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是掠夺者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marauders.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.57,0:37:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掠夺者 杀死所有人的那些家伙 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marauders? The guys that killed everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.16,0:37:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-并非都是 但多数是 -可恶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Not all, but most. - Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.97,0:39:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Asha!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.77,0:39:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Asha!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.32,0:40:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是一切开始的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is where it started,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.53,0:40:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到新伊甸园的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where I first saw New Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.32,0:40:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要看那里头的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't need to look in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.25,0:40:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我别给你看到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You told me not to let you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.29,0:40:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（10月）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.13,0:40:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我想象出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I made it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.05,0:40:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈 裴尔顿医生 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Andre. Dr. Pelton!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.14,0:40:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 你醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay, it's okay. You're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.34,0:41:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（《意大利文艺复兴全史》）
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.10,0:41:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.56,0:41:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我觉得你会想知道一下 裴尔顿医生说他会好起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I--I thought you'd want to know Dr. Pelton thinks he's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.40,0:41:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有持久的脑损伤之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No lasting brain damage or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.61,0:41:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.91,0:41:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你…帮了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}thank you for helping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.21,0:41:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是安德烈的好朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a really good friend to Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.25,0:41:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bess,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.63,0:41:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么关心别人 却不让别人来关心你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you care so much for other people, but you won't let anyone care for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.76,0:41:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.97,0:41:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天已经很够呛了 奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's been a long day, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.99,0:42:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢 -嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, thanks. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.16,0:42:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.33,0:42:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我们吓坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You had us scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.34,0:42:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.30,0:42:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.68,0:42:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时太迫切地想给大家一个未来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was so desperate to give everyone a future...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.23,0:42:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就瞎编了一个 那怎么办 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I made one up?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.27,0:42:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我所拥有的只是一个谎言 我无法领导这列车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't lead this train if all I have is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.70,0:42:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（加拿大）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.00,0:42:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初离开阿塔卡马之后 你们走的是哪条路线 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After the Atacama, what route did you take?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.83,0:42:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会告诉你的 这是怎么回事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm not telling you that. What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.25,0:42:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.34,0:43:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两列列车分开之后 我跟着你们的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After our trains separated, I followed your trail,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.72,0:43:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试图猜测你们的意图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}trying to guess intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.55,0:43:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的近期目的地及长远轨迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}near-term destination versus long-term trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.72,0:43:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟不上你们 所以得半路拦截\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't catch you. I had to intercept.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.81,0:43:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到没 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.90,0:43:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Whoa, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.11,0:43:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 在三个月之后 我觉得自己有了突破\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So about three months in, I thought I caught a break--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.53,0:43:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在马赛附近探测到了轨道切换的信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a track switch signal near Marseille.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.66,0:43:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赶到那里 却没发现你们的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We followed it there but found no sign of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.24,0:43:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 因为我们没在那片大陆上 离法国远着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, yeah, 'cause that was the wrong continent. We were nowhere near France.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.62,0:43:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么问题就来了 如果切换轨道的 不是你们 那会是谁 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So the question is, if it wasn't you, who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.75,0:43:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号出错 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A signal error.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.96,0:43:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不认为那是故障引起的 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I don't think it was a malfunction, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.51,0:43:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那是你母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe it was your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.34,0:43:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅兰妮还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That Melanie is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.95,0:44:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻译：黛拉
